# Changelog
All notable changes to this project will be documented in this file.

The format is based on [Keep a Changelog](https://keepachangelog.com/en/1.1.0/),
and this project adheres to [Semantic Versioning](https://semver.org/spec/v2.0.0.html).

## [Unreleased]
### Added
- CLI enhancements and expanded examples (planned).
- Extended metadata validation for Ghost header (planned).

### Changed
- Internal refactors toward clearer error codes and structured exceptions (planned).

### Fixed
- Pending packaging and docs polish (planned).

---

## [0.5.0] - 2025-08-16
### Added
- Added tacozip_replace_file() function to replace file content while preserving ghost header.
- Documentation updates for new features and usage examples.
- Improved error handling and validation checks in the C core.
- Enhanced Python bindings to support new C functions.


## [0.4.0] - 2025-08-16
### Added
- Replace of my own ZIP implementation with libzip.


## [0.3.0] - 2025-08-10
### Added
- Replace of my own ZIP implementation with libzip.


## [0.3.0] - 2025-08-10
### Added
- First public prototype of C core and Python bindings.

